Class InnerNode<K,V>

All Implemented Interfaces:
Node<K,V>, ComplexPage, MustInitializeOrLoad
public class InnerNode<K,V>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Node<K,V>, ComplexPage

stores pointers to the keys that get push upwards to InnerNodes from LeafPages, as well as the id of nodes in the following order:

NODE_TYPE | NUM_OF_KEYS | NODE_ID | KEY_POINTER | NODE_ID | KEY_POINTER | NODE_ID ...

If the search/insert key is equal to the currently checked key, go to the left.
